VRC+ subscribers can upload and manage custom content types in their inventory, including user icons, photos, custom emojis, custom stickers, and prints. The content types include: User Icons, Photos, Custom Emoji, Custom Stickers and Prints. Users can create them by using the in-client [[Camera]], or through the VRChat website.
